%h1 Top10 Animes

-# anime list
%table.table.table-striped
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Image
      %th Name
      %th Genres
      %th.text-center Episodes
      %th.text-center Finished
      %th Description
      %th class='text-center'>Average Rating
      - if user_signed_in?
        %th.text-center Your Rating
        %th.action
   
  %tbody
    - @animes.each do |anime|
      = render 'top10', anime: anime
      